content: <OpenSearchDescription xmlns="http://a9.com/-/spec/opensearch/1.1/" xmlns:moz="http://www.mozilla.org/2006/browser/search/">         <ShortName>Debian Package Tracker</ShortName>         <Description>                 Lookup a package in the Debian Package Tracker         </Description>         <InputEncoding>UTF-8</InputEncoding>         <Image width="16" height="16" type="image/x-icon">https://tracker.debian.org/favicon.ico</Image>         <Url type="text/html" method="get" template="https://tracker.debian.org/search?package_name={searchTerms}"/>         <Url type="application/x-suggestions+json" method="get" template="https://tracker.debian.org/api/package/search/autocomplete?q={searchTerms}"/> </OpenSearchDescription>
